PHP AMAZON PRODUCT ADVERTISING WRAPPER - VERSION 1.0

A php library class to working with Amazon Product Advertising API.

Using latest version of Amazon Product Advertising API (2011-08-01).

Requirement :

- php 5.3 (min!)
- hash_hmac (to create signature)
- new SimpleXMLElement must be exists

Features :

- Search Operation
- ItemLookup Operation

Todo :

- Power Search ?
- Batch Request ?
- Plugins ? (including feeds) ?

How To Use : https://gist.github.com/2171638
